{"tid":768283,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"人人投考政府咁香港私人市場可以點運作？","createTime":"2018-08-05T08:59:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-05T12:26:58.000Z","uid":107755,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f0150caf7705318d42bb75a95e89a8ccf6f107c9","tid":768283,"uid":107755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T08:59:31.000Z","msg":"好似當年銀行工係一個有光環又搵到錢既行業<br />\n低息買樓，假期醫療人工都屌打政府<br />\n無論由最低到經理級<br />\n咁當然你話ao就應該唔會啦<br />\n<br />\n到今日做政府好似已經調轉哂<br />\n私人市場經歷過太多次炒人<br />\n<br />\n為穩定社會上邊唔同既人<br />\n都會試唔同既政府位<br />\n當然可能我識唔到好高級果d啦<br />\n例如某行aml有個係做過商調警畜既呀頭<br />\n去到咁高先會有保障<br />\n<br />\n其實係我廢識親都係無能力要投靠政府<br />\n或是為錢去讀幼教護士<br />\n定真係香港私人市場真係已經玩完？"},{"pid":"05254a29b7f874466f0139fbe2e1af5cf806aa70","tid":768283,"uid":94828,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T09:01:04.000Z","msg":"請內地專才<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"995bd64710a4660fed02f2a8ed36a1f0392d5014","tid":768283,"uid":107755,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"05254a29b7f874466f0139fbe2e1af5cf806aa70","tid":768283,"uid":94828,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T09:01:04.000Z","msg":"請內地專才<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T09:03:48.000Z","msg":"政府可以吸納所有香港勞動力？<br />\n好似有d慢性毒藥<br />\n令到香港人更易比人取代"},{"pid":"4c009a4c13ec4e97abbc9afdef69322e3e5eb127","tid":768283,"uid":17889,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T09:04:05.000Z","msg":"你肯定你考到eo or above?"},{"pid":"6e973a6b4606e520b3339e7431e0c050407a9310","tid":768283,"uid":107755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c009a4c13ec4e97abbc9afdef69322e3e5eb127","tid":768283,"uid":17889,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T09:04:05.000Z","msg":"你肯定你考到eo or above?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T09:10:51.000Z","msg":"點解討論就要肯定我考到？前設？"},{"pid":"f71ffbe538921f89996b2dd34778e6520522bc78","tid":7